        {
            "title": "歐美債息升   憧憬聯儲局減息",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國國債息率周五升逾3點子以上，歐債息亦升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美國國債。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240103_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美國國債。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240103_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美國國債。</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">通脹預期下降同時美聯儲理事沃勒暗示7月份支持降息，債價報跌債券收益率上漲。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約尾市美國10年期基準國債收益率跌3.58基點，報4.4155%，本周累計上漲0.62基點，整體交投於4.3915%-4.4933%區間。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兩年期美債收益率跌3.54個基點，報3.8691%，本周累跌1.59個基點，整體交投於3.9587%至3.8564%區間。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐市尾盤，德國10年期國債收益率漲2.0個基點，報2.695%，本周累計下跌3.0個基點，整體交投於2.739%-2.662%區間，呈現出W形走勢。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英債價格本周普遍下挫，50年期英債收益率累漲約10個基點。英國10年期國債收益率漲1.9個基點，報4.674%，本周累漲5.3個基點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國10年期國債收益率漲1.9個基點，報3.400%，本周累跌1.5個基點，周一微幅上揚，周二至周五持續低位震蕩。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15103527-%e6%ad%90%e7%be%8e%e5%82%b5%e6%81%af%e5%8d%87-%e6%86%a7%e6%86%ac%e8%81%af%e5%84%b2%e5%b1%80%e6%b8%9b%e6%81%af",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20190902_FI_US-TREASURY-BONDS_US-BOND_FB-1-2-1-1-1-1_source-web_-1-2-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-19 12:15:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "ADR高水95點   美團京東升  夜期曾升破25000關",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據高盛網站，港股ADR較恆指周五收市高水95點或0.38%，報24920點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_03690.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_03690.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：美團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科網股高水，美團 (03690)ADR收市折合港幣133.71元，較香港收市價高5% ; 預計影響恒指55點; 阿里巴巴(09988) ADR較港收市價較港收市價高1.8%，折合港幣117.83元，預計影響恒指35點 ; 京東集團(09618) ADR較香港收市價高3.9%，折合133.18港元，預計影響恒指13點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣518.13元，較香港收市價低0.2%；網易(09999)ADR較香港收市價0.2%，報213.69元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20190503_FI_HSBC__FB-1-1-1-2_source-ap_.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20190503_FI_HSBC__FB-1-1-1-2_source-ap_.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金融股造好，滙控(00005) ADR收市折合港幣98.59元，較香港收市價0.4%  ; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣69.11元，較香港收市價高0.5%  ; 中國平安(02318) ADR收市折合港幣53.16元，較香港收市價0.6% ; 招商銀行(03968) ADR收市折合港幣52.12元，較香港收市價升0.4%，港交所(00388) ADR收市折合港幣430.63元，較香港收市價高0.1% ; 預計合共影響恒指20點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">周五港股大升的中通快遞(02057)，ADR折合港幣148.93元，較香港收市價高低水2.1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中通快遞官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240813_FI_source-web_02057.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中通快遞官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240813_FI_source-web_02057.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中通快遞官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克中國金龍指數升45點或0.6%，報7728點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報24883點，升28點，較昨日恒指收市24825點，高水57點，成交17895張。一度升破25000關，最高見25083。國指夜市期指收報9019點，較昨日國指收市高水33點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15103473-adr%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b495%e9%bb%9e-%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%98%e4%ba%ac%e6%9d%b1%e5%8d%87-%e5%a4%9c%e6%9c%9f%e6%9b%be%e5%8d%87%e7%a0%b425000%e9%97%9c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/HK-STOCK_ADR-1_source-bp_-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-19 11:40:27",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
