        {
            "title": "英股曾升穿9000點  瑞典Saab飆逾16%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15103033&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲股市3大指數走勢不一。石油和天然氣股上升，抵銷重磅醫療保健股下跌的影響，科技股跌0.6%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：德國證交所官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：德國證交所官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：德國證交所官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泛歐指數Stoxx 600周五先升後跌，收市反覆回吐0.01%，報547點，盤初最多曾漲0.46%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數一度升穿9000點，但未能企穩，收報8992點，升19點，升幅0.22%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC40指數收報7822點，升不足1點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數收報24289點，跌81點，跌幅0.33%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報40311點，上揚0.46%或183點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報13989點，微跌0.04%或5點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">瑞典國防股Saab第二季盈利及銷售收入均勝預期，股價急飆16.4%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15103033-%e8%8b%b1%e8%82%a1%e6%9b%be%e5%8d%87%e7%a9%bf9000%e9%bb%9e-%e7%91%9e%e5%85%b8saab%e9%a3%86%e9%80%be16",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-19 10:05:25",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
